        <hl1>A Simple Solution</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>William Shoucair letter on problem of smoking in restaurants (March 15 article)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Here's a simple solution for nonsmokers who are forced to eat at a restaurant that allows smoking. When the check comes, refuse to pay and walk out.</p>
        <p>WILLIAM SHOUCAIR</p>
        <p>Boston</p>
      </block>
